OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDwarfism: Woman's battle   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagainst ignorance starts in
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschools                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman with dwarfism who faces        
OL,6, frequent abuse on the street is        
OL,7, visiting schools in a bid to stamp out 
OL,8, prejudice.                             
OL,10,FDanielle Webb, 23, said changing the   
OL,11,Fminds of ignorant adults was difficult,
OL,12,Fso her focus was on educating children.
OL,14,FDanielle, who is 3ft 11.5in (1.2m),    
OL,15,Fsaid being called names and laughed at 
OL,16,F"just becomes our norm".               
OL,18,FEarlier this week, a documentary about 
OL,19,Fa new drug developed to treat          
OL,20,FDanielle's condition aired on BBC One. 
